<p class="fd-paragraph">
  Intelligent scheduling that combines geographic mapping with appointment management — optimizing visit routes, reducing no-shows, and enabling agents to book, reschedule, and confirm appointments autonomously.
</p>

<h2 class="fd-section-heading">What it does</h2>
<ul class="fd-list">
  <li class="fd-list-item">AI-optimized visit routing for field-based care teams</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Automated appointment reminders and confirmation via SMS or voice</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">Agents can book, reschedule, and cancel appointments without staff involvement</li>
  <li class="fd-list-item">No-show prediction and proactive rescheduling to protect panel capacity</li>
</ul>

<h2 class="fd-section-heading">Why it matters</h2>
<p class="fd-paragraph">
  No-shows and inefficient routing are silent revenue killers in value-based care. Scheduling turns appointment management into an automated, optimized operation.
</p>
